Package: t-digest-doc
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Description: Dunning t-digest implementations - documentation
 The t-digest is a data structure for accurate on-line accumulation of
 rank-based statistics such as quantiles and trimmed means. This package
 contains documentation for the multi-language implementations.

